name: Model Show Dressup
description:
Who will become the world's next International Superstar Ultra-Mega Double-Decker Hypermodel? There is only one answer: the one, the only, SMEFANYE!

Dress up Smefanye in her ten iconic outfits from Lucahjin and ProtonJon's legendary LP of America's Next Top Model!

Includes over ten different outfits and over 80 draggable props!

Music/Background taken from America's Next Top Model for the Wii.

Emotes taken from Lucahjin's twitch channel: twitch.tv/lucahjins

Watch the legendary LP here!
